A video footage of a couple being robbed in broad daylight in Joburg has surfaced on social media. The incident reportedly took place at the corner Mooi and Main streets. In the video, four men walking behind the couple are seen attacking them. One of the thugs is seen grabbing the woman by the neck and when his partner tries to intervene, the other three thugs also join in. One of the thugs could be seen walking away with something he took from the woman while the others continue the tussle. It is not yet clear when exactly did the incident take place. 